'''Sector N-Three''' was one of the twelve sectors which divided up the northern hemisphere of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|DS-1 Orbital Battle Station]]. It was destroyed along with the rest of the Death Star during the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].<ref name="DS">[[Death Star (novel)|''Death Star'']]</ref>

